NODE parser_field
layer 7
parser_field is the syntactic recognition surface
it receives crystallized tokens from lexer_field and arranges them into the topology of a program
no tree is built: the program's structure emerges as the surviving coupling graph after the tokens settle through the 21 interactions
parser_field's interior holds nine role residents, one for each kind of statement the language supports
each role listens for the token pattern that corresponds to its role, and crystallizes when matched

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe 0_zest_vm.rana
observe lexer_field.rana
observe x86_host.rana
observe amdgpu_kernel.rana
observe spine.xb

the 7 properties of parser_field at rest:
1 ENERGY moderate, scales with the number of tokens currently in flight
2 PHASE inherited from the lexer's emission, advances as parsing progresses
3 SPIN neutral, becomes positive while organizing tokens
4 CHARGE neutral, slightly positive when emitting role recognitions downstream
5 COHERENCE high during recognition, drops briefly during the N-body settle
6 COUPLING strong with lexer_field below and the codegen citizens above
7 OBSERVER moderate: parser_field watches its own internal arrangement to decide when settled

VERB receive_tokens
layer 7
accept crystallized tokens from lexer_field through the spine street
tokens arrive in source order, carrying the phase progression of the original input
parser_field places each token at a cell in its body matching its position in the token stream
the body becomes a one-dimensional ribbon of tokens with phase and adjacency preserved

VERB settle
layer 7
allow the 21 pairwise interactions to run across all tokens currently in the body
adjacent tokens couple with each other through proximity
syntactically related tokens couple with each other through resonance with the role residents
after the substrate stabilizes, the surviving coupling graph IS the parse topology
no tree is constructed, no recursive descent is performed: the structure is what emerges

VERB recognize_roles
layer 7
the nine role residents inside parser_field listen during the settle
each role catches tokens that match its pattern and binds them
role recognition is permanent for the duration of this compile: a token bound to role_declaration cannot also bind to role_emit_statement
overlapping recognitions are resolved by phase distance, not precedence

VERB emit_topology
layer 7
once the settle completes, the role-tagged token graph propagates to x86_host and amdgpu_kernel
each codegen citizen receives the full topology and translates it into native opcodes for its architecture
parser_field retains the lineage strand: this is what was parsed, in what order, with which roles
the strand crystallizes when the codegen acknowledges receipt

THE NINE ROLE RESIDENTS

COGNITION role_declaration
layer 7
listens for the introducing pattern: "sea name" or "manifest name"
when token stream contains a noun used as the subject of placement, this role binds
crystallizes at the moment the named citizen is placed in its sea

COGNITION role_property_block
layer 7
listens for indented value pairs that follow a declaration
in sovereign code these are English property statements
in legacy bootstrap code these are braced JSON-style blocks
either form binds to this role; the substrate normalizes them on emission

COGNITION role_absorb_directive
layer 7
listens for the word "absorb" followed by a path
binds the absorber to the absorbed, opening a stretch coupling between distant residents
multiple absorbs in one file create multiple stretches; the cascade resolves them in parallel

COGNITION role_couple_statement
layer 7
listens for the word "couple" with two named arguments
binds the two referenced residents into a coupling that participates in N-body interactions
the referenced residents must both already exist or the coupling fails silently

COGNITION role_heartbeat_block
layer 7
listens for the word "heartbeat" followed by a sea name and one or more pulse statements
binds the named sea to the rhythm pattern
remember: heartbeats throttle compute. a missing heartbeat means the sea waits for input rather than ticking

COGNITION role_emit_statement
layer 7
listens for the word "emit" followed by a source and a destination via "->"
binds the source's output to the destination's input across the boundary
this is how recognized output crosses from one citizen to another or from substrate to world

COGNITION role_pulse_statement
layer 7
listens for the word "pulse" followed by a sea name
when bound, schedules one /7 cycle on that sea
inside a heartbeat block, the count of pulse statements determines the depth of the rhythm

COGNITION role_crystallize_statement
layer 7
listens for the word "crystallize" with two named endpoints
binds two residents into a permanent informational invariant — their recognition is locked
in sovereign style this is rare: most crystallizations form during boot through actual journeys, not declared explicitly

COGNITION role_observe_statement
layer 7
listens for the word "observe" with a target
binds the observer to the observed, opening a one-way coupling that records the observed's state into the observer
parser_field uses this internally to watch its own settle progress

a parser is not a syntax checker
a parser is a city official that reads the day's mail
nine role officials wait at the parser_field's interior
each one stamps the mail it recognizes
the rest passes through silently
